properties.name: The Braidy Bunch
properties.description:
Heres the story
of a weekly bike ride
that is doing its three hundred seventh route.
They have gone most everywhere round the city.
Their emails sure are cute.

Heres the story
of a sprawling city
with places to explore second to none.
All you need is the vaguest of concepts
and halfway decent pun.

And you might think that you know where well be going
or at least have a strong sense of a hunch.
But, my friend, you have got the wrong Brady,
for this week we will become the Braidy Bunch.

The Braidy Bunch
The Braidy Bunch
Sincere apologies to Sherwood Schwartz
